    <summaries>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>00</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2005-06-07</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Introduced in House</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2005-07-28T19:59:30Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Prohibits any person engaged in the retail sales of cigarette products to place cigarette products in the general merchandise areas of a retail sales facility and within reach of customers. Requires all cigarette products sold at retail to be placed under or behind a counter where they may be accessible only to a salesperson.</p> <p>Treats a violation of such prohibition as an unfair or deceptive act or practice under the Federal Trade Commission Act and gives the Federal Trade Commission (FTC) enforcement authority.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
    <title>To require cigarette products to be placed under or behind the counter in retail sales.</title>
